<plot>As digital projection technology replaces century-old projectors in theatres across the country, motion picture projectionists prepare to make their last stand against the encroaching forces of technology. BEHIND THE GLASS traces the evolution and decline of this romanticized craft as it profiles projectionists from drive-ins, movie palaces and multiplexes who lead the fight against the cheapening of America's favorite form of entertainment.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063708</url></doc>
